                    S = &int; d<sup>26</sup>X &radic;(-G) [R + <span style="text-decoration: overline;">&Psi;</span><sub>P</sub> (i&Gamma;<sup>M</sup>D<sub>M</sub> - m)&Psi;<sub>P</sub>]
                </div>
                <div class="formula-controls">
                    <span class="foundation-badge pm-specific">Master Action</span>
