            <p>
                The following presents the complete hierarchy of Lagrangians from the 26D bulk action down to 4D observable
                physics. Each level emerges naturally from dimensional reduction
                and gauge fixing, with fermionic primacy maintained throughout.
            </p>

            <h3>1. Master Bulk Action (26D)</h3>
