                    Master Bulk Action: Fermionic Primacy
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="physics-note">
                <h4>Fermionic Primacy</h4>
                <p>
                    The Pneuma spinor &Psi;<sub>P</sub> is <strong>not</strong> a matter field on a fixed background.
                    The fermionic term sources the Einstein equations: R<sub>MN</sub> = T<sub>MN</sub>[&Psi;<sub>P</sub>].
                    Spacetime geometry emerges from Pneuma condensates, embodying true fermionic primacy.
                </p>
            </div>

